	   <tr><td colspan=2>was wondering what you guys think about twisting Hymn of restoration, either soloing or PvPing, I try to keep the group or myself healed up while fighting, usually twisting anthem/heal/chords/bellow is that wrong to do?, should I concentrate on doing more damage and just use the heal song on down time, also I was thinking of being a 2 hand slash bard so I can switch between weapon and insturments in melee battle easier, but I have not seen any 2hs for a bard, I really don't like the fact of just running around and twisting DoT's/DD's/snare, can anyone give me the best strategy at soloing and grouping, PvP is not even worth it yet because im only lvl 18 and usually getting taken out by lvl 30s or higher, I twist usually grouped anthem/heal/chords/bellow while switching weapons and instruments I don't solo much anymore, I soloed from lvl 1 - 11 and found it hard after that since all I have is newbie gear, keep in mind that Sullon Zek is a new server and there aren't any uber twinks running around. Also where can I get a list of the instruments and which ones are an upgrade from the old one in their class, like a table from worst to best in the percussion line that will actually increase the effect of those types of songs<br><br>Endevor<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
